<p>Hi <%= @resource.first_name %>!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password.  Hopefully that's you!  Otherwise, you must have some enemies out there.</p>

<p>Your password won't change until you click the link below and create a new one.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>